&lt;li&gt;You have the ability to juggle multiple client/customer interactions and deadlines simultaneously&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are detail oriented and have the agility to work with, develop relationships with and influence a diverse set of cross-functional stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
