&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience processing payroll in an HRIS system (preferrably Workday)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with equity administration and taxation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced proficiency in Microsoft Excel (i.e. VLOOKUP, Pivot Tables, etc.) and familiarity with Google Suite&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to handle high-volume data accurately and efficiently&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective communication skill and experience communicating with a diverse employee base&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills and attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a Bachelor’s degree or equivalent experience&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a desire to learn, develop an existing skill set, and take on more responsibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Extra Credit&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience with international payroll and/or equity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience with equity administration in EquatePlus/Computershare&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience handling tickets in Zendesk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
