&lt;p&gt;Building on 10 years of experience in the US, Flatiron’s international team is scaling Flatiron’s approach in new countries. Streamlined teams in each market are establishing partnerships with local cancer care providers and developing high-quality real-world data for researchers around the world. Data Scientists are embedded in those teams and play a key role in understanding our data partners’ source data and conducting exploratory data analyses to support data-driven decision-making. They build research-grade data sets and leverage a breadth of tools, including AI, to develop approaches to enrich our data models, maximise data quality and increase efficiency and robustness of our pipelines. .&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
