&lt;li&gt;Conduct exploratory analyses to define source data ingestion approaches that meet our quality bar; define business logic to transform new source data into Flatiron’s common data model.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply and validate LLM-based approaches to process unstructured electronic health record data at scale to enhance our real-world data products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with software engineers to design, implement and automate scalable data pipelines, utilising internal or off-the-shelf external AI tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
